title: Amy Confronts Thieves That Stole Her Kids’ Bikes + Lunchbox Takes Over Walmart Intercom And Sings Tina Turner
itunes:title: Amy Confronts Thieves That Stole Her Kids’ Bikes + Lunchbox Takes Over Walmart Intercom And Sings Tina Turner
description:
Amy confronts a couple kids who stole her children’s bikes. Lunchbox takes over the intercom at a Walmart and attempts to sing Tina Turner for 60 seconds. Amy gives herself the shock collar as punishment for spoiling the ending for a movie Bobby wanted to see.
